import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import 'react-bootstrap/Collapse'
import 'animate.css'
import {  BrowserRouter as Router,  Routes,  Route,  Link} from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './Home'
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      {/* dark navbar */}
      <Navbar bg='dark' expand='lg'>
        <Container>
          <Navbar.Brand color='light'>Typed.js</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls='basic-navbar-nav' bg='light'/>
          <Navbar.Collapse id='basic-navbar-nav'>
            <Nav className='ms-auto'>
              <Nav.Link><Link to='/' className='text-decoration-none'>Home</Link></Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link><Link to='/about' className='text-decoration-none'>About</Link></Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link><Link to='/contact' className='text-decoration-none'>Contact</Link></Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
          </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
      </Navbar>
      <Routes>
        <Route exact path='/' element={<Home/>}/>
      </Routes>
  </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
